                  <fr:link href="/greenberg-harper-alg-topo/" title="Algebraic Topology" uri="https://juan-mad.github.io/greenberg-harper-alg-topo/" display-uri="greenberg-harper-alg-topo" type="local" />
                </fr:meta>
              </fr:frontmatter>
              <fr:mainmatter><html:p>Una <html:em>homotopía de cadenas</html:em> entre <fr:link href="/HL-0002/" title="Morfismo de complejos de cadenas" uri="https://juan-mad.github.io/HL-0002/" display-uri="HL-0002" type="local">morfismos de cadenas</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f=\{f_q\colon C_q\rightarrow C_q'\}]]></fr:tex> y <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[g=\{g_q\colon C_q\rightarrow C_q'\}]]></fr:tex> es una secuencia <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[D=\{D_q\colon C_q\rightarrow C_{q+1}'\}]]></fr:tex> de homomorfismos tales que <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[\partial _{q+1}'D_q + D_{q-1}\partial _q = f_q = g_q.]]></fr:tex></html:p>
  <html:center><fr:resource hash="22dbe70f240e1ff3d5bd059b6d076679"><fr:resource-content><html:img src="/22dbe70f240e1ff3d5bd059b6d076679.svg" /></fr:resource-content><fr:resource-source type="latex" part="preamble"><![CDATA[\usepackage {quiver, amsopn, amssymb, mathrsfs}]]></fr:resource-source><fr:resource-source type="latex" part="body"><![CDATA[\begin {tikzcd}
	{C_{q+1}} && {C_q} && {C_{q-1}} \\
	\\
	{C_{q-1}'} && {C_q'} && {C_{q-1}'}
	\arrow ["{\partial _{q+1}}", from=1-1, to=1-3]
	\arrow ["{f_{q+1}-g_{q+1}}"', from=1-1, to=3-1]
	\arrow ["{\partial _q}", from=1-3, to=1-5]
	\arrow ["{D_q}"', from=1-3, to=3-1]
	\arrow ["{f_q-g_q}"', from=1-3, to=3-3]
	\arrow ["{D_{q-1}}"', from=1-5, to=3-3]
	\arrow ["{f_{q-1}-g_{q-1}}", from=1-5, to=3-5]
	\arrow ["{\partial _{q+1}'}", from=3-1, to=3-3]
